637bb18d46f0d88cd71de9a46c4762","tid":907304,"uid":215601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13ad898b9914ba63a53199f82f6b573e2edfe08f","tid":907304,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b06159cd041ab1d3e6efe6c750f4b3ba67ab144c","tid":907304,"uid":215601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T16:57:02.000Z","msg":"總會有一兩個願意聽你講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n我啲朋友都係FG嚟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T17:02:41.000Z","msg":"我好怕講得多佢地嫌我煩<br />\n同埋我講黎講去都係同一件事，講得多都口臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T17:13:24.000Z","msg":"做朋友都係give and take嘅，呢個時候佢聽你講之後你咪聽返人講啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T17:33:41.000Z","msg":"我唔識得點樣同人傾訴自己 既情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果話我好憎一個人，我就識講，識屌佢<br />\n你話返工好大壓力又好，老闆仆街又好，我都識呻<br />\n但我唔識點樣同朋友呻自己係外國冇朋友係度好寂寞，<br />\n我係ig見到其他人一班朋友周圍去，我心底好羡幕佢地，<br />\n覺得自己好冇用，之前做錯左好多決定，浪費左好多機會，我本身成績差，一直覺得呢個係我翻身機會，我好睇重呢件事，接受唔到失敗<br />\n仲有半年就要畢業，接受唔到帶住遺憾離去<br />\n<br />\n講白D<br />\n我最憎既人係我自己時，我就唔知點樣同其他人呻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\np.s.多謝你肯理我"},{"pid":"38f89d2edef45ff26f82dd01ec77ced74629a972","tid":907304,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T18:11:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f506a532f8ced46421b03edb4edc696bbca8f7b","tid":907304,"uid":31414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T18:25:08.000Z","msg":"外國撚<br />\n憂心既都唔會講<br />\n怕佢地擔心"},{"pid":"edd17b604a5e6f47395f0260831170bc72436bed","tid":907304,"uid":215601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0a5619f6ec32e0c322a25607e8081e79ccc120b","tid":907304,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fc2ee2a43637bb18d46f0d88cd71de9a46c4762","tid":907304,"uid":215601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13ad898b9914ba63a53199f82f6b573e2edfe08f","tid":907304,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T17:02:41.000Z","msg":"我好怕講得多佢地嫌我煩<br />\n同埋我講黎講去都係同一件事，講得多都口臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T17:13:24.000Z","msg":"做朋友都係give and take嘅，呢個時候佢聽你講之後你咪聽返人講啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T17:33:41.000Z","msg":"我唔識得點樣同人傾訴自己 既情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果話我好憎一個人，我就識講，識屌佢<br />\n你話返工好大壓力又好，老闆仆街又好，我都識呻<br />\n但我唔識點樣同朋友呻自己係外國冇朋友係度好寂寞，<br />\n我係ig見到其他人一班朋友周圍去，我心底好羡幕佢地，<br />\n覺得自己好冇用，之前做錯左好多決定，浪費左好多機會，我本身成績差，一直覺得呢個係我翻身機會，我好睇重呢件事，接受唔到失敗<br />\n仲有半年就要畢業，接受唔到帶住遺憾離去<br />\n<br />\n講白D<br />\n我最憎既人係我自己時，我就唔知點樣同其他人呻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\np.s.多謝你肯理我"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T18:40:51.000Z","msg":"明呀，我係外國基本上都係自己一個人都覺得寂寞<br />\n真係唔知點同身邊嘅人講嘅話，放上嚟呢到都係一個辦法啊，起碼呢到應該會有差唔多經歷嘅人<br />\n雖然幫唔到啲咩，但係起碼講咗出嚟會好小小<br />\n巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de4b61abfdf7d27457b5ae853b3a7123155c66ce","tid":907304,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T03:57:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9df6782f63a45b184ecee7f303a19317379e7356","tid":907304,"uid":55888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T04:00:26.000Z","msg":"冇試過同屋企人講<br />\n屋企人同啲朋友都以為我一直都好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/